snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited – Reforging Orsinium
snippet.description:
Watch our latest trailer "Reforging Orsinium" for a first look at the upcoming Orsinium DLC game pack for The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited, coming to PC/Mac on November 2nd, Xbox One on November 17th, and PlayStation®4 on November 18th.

For more information about The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited, visit our website: http://www.elderscrollsonline.com/en-us/esotu  

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline   
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+ElderScrollsOnline/  

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence
